============================================================

Concept:     LSTM
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Gating mechanisms solve vanishing gradient in sequences
Year:        1997
Researchers: Hochreiter/Schmidhuber
Applications:NLP, speech, time series
Related:     GRU, RNN, gates, cell state

Concept:     Diffusion Model
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Learns to reverse a noise-adding process for generation
Year:        2020
Researchers: Ho et al.
Applications:Image/video/audio generation (Stable Diffusion)
Related:     DDPM, score matching, noise schedule

Concept:     Word Embeddings
Category:    Representation
Definition:  Dense vectors where semantic similarity = vector proximity
Year:        2013
Researchers: Mikolov et al.
Applications:NLP, recommendation, search
Related:     Word2Vec, GloVe, BERT embeddings

